<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.2.8">
<l>kompupōl cītai poruṭṭilaṅ kainaka</l>
<l>ramperi yuyttavar tāḷiṇai mēlaṇi</l>
<l>vampaviḻ taṇṇantu ḻāymalark kēyivaḷ</l>
<l>nampumā ṉāṉitaṟ keṉceykē ṉaṅkaimīr</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For the cool Tulsi blossoms opening in the new rain</l>
<l>[that are the] decoration on the foot-pair of him, who sent arrow flames</l>
<l>to the city of Laṅka for the sake of twig-like Sītā,</l>
<l>she longs. What will I do about this, you ladies?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
